caption_original: Today, the Government of Canada announced the transfer of the Igloo Tag management to the Inuit Art Foundation (IAF). This will benefit Inuit artists and help preserve the values of Inuit cultural heritage for generations to come. The Government of Canada also released a study on the impact of the Inuit arts economy that was produced to help develop a policy to support Inuit arts and artists in Canada. http://ow.ly/jxTY30dA0M6
